        <div class="span-small-12 offset-small-6 offset-medium-0 margin-top-50">
            <span class="flo-title">HOW DID<br/>
            FLO RIDA GET<br/>
            THIS RIPPED?</span>
        </div>
        <div class="span-large-6 span-medium-7 span-small-12 offset-small-6 offset-medium-5 offset-large-5 margin-top-100">
            <a class="button button-primary" href="{{ path("downloads_product_flomersion") }}" id="flomersion-button">Platinum Club</a>
